author: ErwanB

name: videosurveillance
description:
# Pitch

Vous etes un cyber detective.
On vous propose un contrat dont la remuneration de 10 BTC depasse largement ce que l'on vous propose habituellement.
Pourtant votre comanditaire vous demande de recuperer le flux video d'une camera de vidosurveillance !
Vous n'en revenez pas.
Quelle genre de video peut bien valoir un tel prix ?!
Votre equipier a deja pris la main sur un switch et vous donne la capture wireshark d'un trafic reseau qu'il a pu intercepter.
Il dit qu'avec ca vous devriez pouvoir entrer...
#
But du jeu

Vous disposez d'une capture wireshark, final.pcapng qui consituera votre point d'entree sur un reseau compose de plusieurs machines.
Vous devez analyser le pcap pour touver le rseau, compromettre deux machines au sein de ce rseau et recuper un flux video.
Le flag se trouve dans le flux video.
Bonne chance !

https://sthatic.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/Erwan01/final_sthack.pcapng

author: Laluka

name: Dwidder
description:
Your client Muskrat mandates you to investigate a case of corruption in the social networking world.

The takeover of the company Pwipper has failed despite months of preparation and consultation because of the presence of fake accounts on the platform.


A competitor company, Dwidder, seems to stop at nothing and would have launched a campaign to create fake accounts on the Pwipper platform. 

Dwidder's organization is rather mafia-like and is said to be behind several sabotages.

Its administrator seems to have shady practices in terms of code and business... He is however a great defender of open source.

Find the secret information of the administrator of Dwidder and put an end to this network.
Also be prepared to see some strange things.

[Challenge](https://dwidder.sthack.fr)
author: hessman

name: Catch the bird, a trip from web to IRL.
description:
----------------------------------------------


[![](https://documentation.raspisms.fr/_static/logo.png)](https://raspisms.fr)



This challenge is sponsored by [RaspiSMS, the open source solution to send and receive SMS by internet.](https://raspisms.fr)



----------------------------------------------




⠀

⠀

⠀


This time I think Archer have got himself involved in something far to big for him.














 
Last time I've seen him he seemed agitated, anxious, he kept telling about that man he was following, how he felt it had been made, and something about Malta and some bird statuette. That was 9 days ago and I haven't heard from Miles since then. 


It seems strange, but it wouldn't be the first time he didn't give news for days until  he woke up to some unknown county of this damn country, with an empty bottle of the worst whisky  and a skull full of the finest hangover. The guy love the bottle to much, and she didn't returned him so well. Yet, I could tell something was off, it didn't felt right. 



That was until this morning, when a post card arrived at the bureau mailbox.
![Postcard](https://sthatic.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/Ajani01/post-card.png "Postcard")
At first sight it's just a simple postcard to tell me he need to take some vacations right ? But here's the thing, Miles never lived at the 101.10 Marconi street...

 If Archer  ask for my help then it must really be serious. I need to find where this statuette is, and judging by the postcard I must hurry, 'cause whomever have the damn bird, it seems like he want to sell it.
